title: Printing use to work but is no longer working from phone.
content:
I have an HP wireless printer that i use to print emails/docs from my phone with no issues.  The printer still shows in the list to select but recently (last 3 days) i am not able to print any longer.  I get an error "Sorry that didn't work.  Try again".  I am not sure if a required app to print was removed but i am not able to print from any app on my Pixel 3a.

Help please?!?!?!?
